name: The Golden Temple stills vol 7 "Tension"
description:
Taavi Varm (2020) | 8K (7680x4320) jpg | www.varmstudio.com

This piece is a still-frame render from video created for the ballet "The Golden Tempel" inspired by a novel of Yukio Mishima and choreography by Teet Kask. Ballet premiered in December 2020 in Estonian National Opera and was nominated for best ballet @ Estonian Theatre Awards.
